name: Mushroom, admirer, tears and artificial love
description:
The case when you meet your fan and he wants you, but you understand that you don't really need him and you are not very interested. But still you decide to once again use this "game" for your own purposes. The admirer looks at you with enthusiastic eyes, and you know that tomorrow he will sob from this whole situation. But you almost don't care. And you give boring artificial love to this unfortunate man.
